      <title>特朗普辩护律师与法官就华盛顿特区案件选举时间发生争执</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/trump-defense-spars-with-judge-over-election-timing-in-dc-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[审理针对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的 2020 年选举干预起诉案的联邦法官表示，这位前总统的辩护团队试图拖延此案，因为他正在为 11 月 5 日的大选重返白宫而竞选，而他的律师对这一说法提出异议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/trump-defense-spars-with-judge-over-election-timing-in-dc-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:08:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普承诺对企业征收 15% 的税，并任命马斯克负责联邦审计</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/trump-vows-15-corporate-tax-and-taps-musk-for-federal-audit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普承诺降低企业税率、削减监管并对联邦政府进行审计，他采纳了亿万富翁支持者埃隆·马斯克提出的想法，并向纽约的华尔街和企业领袖宣传了他的议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/trump-vows-15-corporate-tax-and-taps-musk-for-federal-audit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:49:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自由派旧金山驱逐移民以应对芬太尼危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-05/san-francisco-s-fentanyl-crisis-triggers-migrant-deportation-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着致命毒品给人们和经济带来的巨大损失日益加重，该市采取了更为强硬的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-05/san-francisco-s-fentanyl-crisis-triggers-migrant-deportation-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 15:45:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新总理上任 泰国立法者批准 1110 亿美元预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/thai-lawmakers-approve-111-billion-budget-as-new-pm-takes-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国议会下院通过了 10 月份开始的财政年度 3.75 万亿泰铢（1110 亿美元）的预算，这将使新任总理巴东丹·西那瓦能够增加政府支出，加速刚刚开始的经济复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/thai-lawmakers-approve-111-billion-budget-as-new-pm-takes-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:52:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水危机暴露英国脆弱性 召开投资者会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/uk-calls-investor-meeting-as-thames-crisis-exposes-fragility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国高级部长将于下周接待投资者，以吸引资金进入英国水务行业。近几个月来，英国最大水务供应商泰晤士水务公司持续的财务困境暴露了该行业的脆弱性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/uk-calls-investor-meeting-as-thames-crisis-exposes-fragility</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:47:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班将在最严峻的选举考验前放弃预算紧缩政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/hungary-s-orban-to-ditch-austerity-before-toughest-election-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 准备在选举前撕毁其预算整合承诺，以刺激支出浪潮，而选举将成为他十多年来执政以来最艰难的一次选举。福林兑欧元的涨幅被抹去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/hungary-s-orban-to-ditch-austerity-before-toughest-election-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:38:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡车司机封锁道路 哥伦比亚面临粮食和燃料短缺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/colombia-faces-food-and-fuel-shortages-as-trucker-strike-bites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚卡车司机抗议封锁道路已持续第四天，导致全国范围内出现粮食和燃料短缺的警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/colombia-faces-food-and-fuel-shortages-as-trucker-strike-bites</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:30:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
